<li><i><a href="/wiki/Arrow_of_God" title="Arrow of God">Arrow of God</a></i>, (1964)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/A_Man_of_the_People" title="A Man of the People">A Man of the People</a></i>, (1966)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Anthills_of_the_Savannah" title="Anthills of the Savannah">Anthills of the Savannah</a></i>, (1987)</li>
</ul>
